course.subject: SBMT
course.name: GNAM Small Network Online Courses
course.description: The Small Network Online Courses (SNOC) enroll a select group of students engaged in a common effort to build management skills. They are offered virtually by a member school of the Global Network for Advanced Management (GNAM), connecting students online for lectures and discussions, and collaborative team projects, developing teamwork skills and cross-cultural perspectives. The course may be repeated for credits if the SNOCs taken are offered by different schools. Graded PP, P or F.
